import React from 'react'
import CheckoutProduct from '../CheckoutProduct/index'
import {Checkouth1, CheckoutList} from './style'


const Checkout = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Checkouth1>Your Basket</Checkouth1>
            <CheckoutList>
                <CheckoutProduct/>
            </CheckoutList>
        </>
    )
}

export default Checkout
